name: Jordan 5 Retro Bluebird (W)
description: The Wmns Air Jordan 5 Retro 'Blue Bird' features a vibrant look on its classic basketball construction. The shoe's upper emerges in suede, finished in Photo Blue and secured by molded TPU eyelets and a lace lock. The quarter panel includes clear netting, while more blue marks the Jumpman on the silver tongue. Underfoot, the signature shark-tooth detailing also appears in silver, with visible Air in the heel offering cushioning. A translucent rubber outsole provides traction.
